6. Pricing, Subscription & Guarantees

Price Justification
	•	[Premium fabrics]
	•	[Ethical manufacturing]
	•	[Durability compared to alternatives]
	•	[Unique design elements]

Guarantees
	•	Free exchanges
	•	Fit guarantee
	•	30–90 day wear-test guarantee
	•	Lifetime repairs (if applicable)

Subscription / Membership Perks
	•	Early access to drops
	•	Exclusive colorways
	•	Limited-edition capsules
	•	Loyalty rewards

⸻

7. Conversion Messaging Frameworks

Comfort Messaging
	•	“Comfort you’ll reach for every day.”
	•	“Softness that gets better with every wash.”

Fit Messaging
	•	“Engineered to fit real bodies.”
	•	“Your new go-to piece for any outfit.”

Quality Messaging
	•	“Crafted to outlast fast fashion.”
	•	“Premium fabrics without the premium markup.”

Performance Messaging
	•	“Moves with you, never against you.”
	•	“Stay cool, dry, and comfortable all day long.”

Sustainability Messaging
	•	“Better for you, better for the planet.”
	•	“Made with responsibly sourced materials.”

Objection Handlers
	•	“Free exchanges if the fit isn’t perfect.”
	•	“Thousands of 5-star reviews.”
	•	“Designed to last, season after season.”

⸻

8. FAQ & Objection Handling (Apparel)

“How does it fit?”

Answer: [Fit notes, body type info, model details]

“Will it shrink?”

Answer: [Fabric behavior + care instructions]

“Is the material high quality?”

Answer: [Fabric composition + certifications]

“What if the size isn’t right?”

Answer: [Exchange policy]

“Is it worth the price?”

Answer: [Longevity, quality, fair trade, better materials]

⸻

9. Content Creation Guidelines (Apparel)
	1.	Lead with feel + fit.
	2.	Use sensory language (soft, structured, buttery, breathable).
	3.	Show movement and comfort.
	4.	Highlight versatility (work → weekend → travel).
	5.	Use lifestyle storytelling with rich visuals.
	6.	Always tie material → feeling → identity.
	7.	Incorporate social proof in all flows.

⸻

10. Versioning & Updates

Update when:
	•	New fabrics or colorways launch
	•	Seasonal collections change
	•	Fit adjustments are made
	•	Customer reviews reveal new benefit angles
	•	Sustainability practices evolve

